sources.title: Seasin's Greetinks! (1933)
sources.description: Popeye skates over to Olive's house to give her a Christmas present: ice skates of her own. While he's teaching her, Bluto skates up and gets fresh; of course, Popeye fights him. When Olive rejects Bluto again, he sends her careening on an ice floe towards a waterfall. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/seasins-greetinks-1933/
